@node introduction "Description"
@toc main

@{b}Introduction@{ub}

This program will stop drives DF0:, DF1:, DF2: and DF3: from clicking. The drives will continue working normally.
@endnode
@node installation "Installation"
@toc main

@{b}Installation@{ub}

Copy the program to anywhere you like, for example the C: directory.
@endnode
@node usage "Usage"
@toc main

@{b}Usage@{ub}

The program is CLI only. Simply start it and it will make the drives stop clicking. There is no possibility to selectively stop 3 or less drives from clicking, it's all or nothing. I have done this because it seemed a bit useless to only make one drive stop clicking.
@endnode
